Phil jokes that he’s a small person trapped in a tall persons body 
But I don’t think we could handle a smaller phil 
Dan would...
body:
Phil jokes that he’s a small person trapped in a tall persons body

But I don’t think we could handle a smaller phil

Dan would always hold things above his head where phil couldn’t reach

And phil would attempt to climb dan to grab it from dan

And we’d have a twitter thread of dans creep shots of Phil in various situations where being short has inconvenienced him, including pics of Phil climbing on the counter to steal Dan’s cereal

by larryphanlinson

The year is 1901. Philip Lester is the heir to a grand estate in the Scottish countryside. Daniel Howell is the youngest son of a rich American businessman. When fate leads them to meet at a prestigious London boarding school, they find themselves growing closer and closer together, in ways they couldn’t dream. But sometimes fate isn’t in your favor forever.
